Breeding male.description: Blackpoll Warblers have a solid black cap and a white cheek unlike Black-and-white Warblers.

Adult.description: Although often seen creeping along trees like Black-and-White Warblers, Yellow-throated Warblers have bright yellow throats unlike Black-and-white Warblers.

Adult/immature.description: Brown Creepers have a similar behavior to Black-and-white Warblers, but they are smaller brown-and-white birds, with a longer tail that they prop against the tree for support, which Black-and-white Warblers don't do.
